methods.registerTimeSource:
Register the time column and rowSet from a new table to replay. Most users will use replay,
 replayGrouped, or replayGroupedLastBy instead of this function.

:param rowSet: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.utils.RowSet) - table rowSet
:param timestampSource: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.ColumnSource<io.deephaven.engine.tables.utils.DateTime>) - column source containing time information.
methods.setTime:
Sets the current replay time.

:param updatedTime: (long) - new replay time.
